# Event wraps an internal Condition to implement a simple boolean flag; Barrier
# synchronizes a fixed count of threads at a rendezvous point; local provides
# per-thread attribute namespaces via attribute access. All three are structural
# and organizational primitives with no formatting, bytes, or path protocol.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

